you could use it as a container image

`podman run quay.io/containers/skopeo:v1.1.0` {favorite skopeo command}

I'm not sure that v1.1.1 has reached stable yet, after it does it too will be there.  Reference [here](https://github.com/containers/skopeo/tree/master/contrib/skopeoimage)
